urls.title: Audio descriptive commentary makes Qatar 2022 accessible for blind fans
urls.description: Faisal Kohaji has been a football fan for as long as he can remember. Being blind has not stopped him from enjoying the game. However, his enjoyment has improved markedly during the FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022™ thanks to audio descriptive commentary.
